The Debian Package network-env
------------------------------

1. Run nenv-create ENV_LOGICAL_NAME.

2. Add configuration file depending on individual network enviroments 
   to the set controled by this tool.
   For example,

       nenv-addfile /etc/network/interfaces
       nenv-addfile /etc/mailname
       nenv-addfile /etc/defaultdomain

3. nenv-change ENV_LOGICAL_NAME.

